{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_06_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 目指せスリクスさん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さとみによるユニットの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡA few days after the members of the unit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "メンバーが決まって数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "were chosen by Satomi",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私って子供っぽいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it true that I look like a kid?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどうしたんだ？　何か言われたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's all this about all of a sudden? Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃないんですけど……今回のユニットは\n各グループの最年少が集まってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that‚ but… In this unit‚\nthe youngest members from each group are gathered‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのすみれちゃん、リズノワのこころちゃん\n月ストのすずちゃん、サニピの雫ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's Sumire-chan from TRINITYAiLE‚ Kokoro-chan from LizNoir‚\nSuzu-chan from Moon Tempest‚ and Shizuku-chan from Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな年少組のユニットに\nどうして私が選ばれたのかなって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wondered why I was chosen for a unit\nwith such young members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "年齢なら、琴乃ちゃんや瑠依さん、葵さんも\n私と同い年ですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In terms of age‚ Kotono-chan‚ Rui-san‚ and\nAoi-san are the same age as me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "私より年下の優ちゃんや芽衣ちゃんもいるのに\nみんなを差し置いて年少組に交じるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even Yu-chan and Mei-chan‚ who are younger than me‚ are there…\nI can't believe I joined the younger group without everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私ってそんなに子供っぽく見えるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I look that childish?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.566666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかして千紗は、自分の見た目が）\n（子供っぽいことを気にしているのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is Chisa worried about her appearance）\n（That she looks childish?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "前にも似た企画があっただろう？　あの時、千紗は\nお姉さんとしてみんなを支えてくれたじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Remember that similar project we had before?\nYou supported everyone like an older sister back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "見た目のことなんて気にしなくていい\n大切なのは外見より中身だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about your appearance.\nWhat matters is what's inside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、{user}さんも\n私の見た目は子供っぽいと思ってるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}-san also thinks\nI look childish‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それは……子供っぽいというか……ほら\n童顔で可愛らしいところも千紗の魅力だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's just… It's not childish‚ but… You see…\nYour younger and cute appearance is part of your charm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "……意地悪を言ってごめんなさい\n見た目が子供っぽいことは自分でも分かってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry for being mean.\nI understand that I look childish myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "誤解しないで下さいね\n可愛いらしいって言われるのが嫌な訳じゃないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't get me wrong.\nI don't hate being called cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、いつまでも子供っぽいのは\nどうなのかなって思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just that I wonder if being childish forever\nIs a good thing or not…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は大人っぽくなりたいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you want to become more mature‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、内面だけじゃなくて\n見た目や雰囲気も大人っぽくなりたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ not just internally‚\nbut also in appearance and vibe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どうしたら大人の雰囲気を出せるんでしょうか\n見当もつかないです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have no idea\nhow to have a mature vibe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（外見や雰囲気が大人っぽくなる方法か……）\n（確かに、今の千紗には難しいかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ways to appear more mature…）\n（It might be difficult for Chisa in her current state.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3677520994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.666666619,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4313.3333809999785,
