      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.666666619
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.666666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "このマーケットは利回りがレバレッジでロスカットの\nTOBがインサイダー取引……あ、おはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This market involves leverage and loss-cutting\nTOB for insider trading… Oh‚ good morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5050101094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8000070731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗？　一体何をしているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa? What on earth are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8000070731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、株価をチェックしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was checking stock prices.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9333404064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.0333404064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、大人っぽくなりたいって話をしましたよね\nあの後、雫ちゃんに相談してみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday‚ we talked about wanting to be more grown-up‚ right?\nAfter that‚ I consulted with Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら雫ちゃんが、星見プロで一番大人っぽい\nスリクスさんを参考にしたらどうかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She suggested that I take a cue from ⅢX-san‚\nwho's the most adult-like at Hoshimi Prods…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.8000070731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それでfranさんの真似をしたのか\nちなみにさっき呟いていたのはどういう意味なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ it seems that you were imitating fran.\nBy the way‚ what did you mean by your murmuring earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
